{"type":"answer","id":22208,"parentType":"question","parentId":5278,"uid":3217,"contents":"可以啊，参考下图，直球反共不太吼，坠好拉一些墙内明星下水，扩大影响力，以低级红高级黑的方式进行反共。手段可以参考恶俗和支那wiki的高雅创作。一旦这个idol被拉清单了，顺便还能给一些无脑跪舔idol的野蛮粉红进行大脑升级。<br>\n（<a href=\"https://mohu.pincong.rocks/article/501\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">原图出处</a>）<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/d2ODPly.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d2ODPly.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/d2ODPly.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/aukYmBh.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aukYmBh.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/aukYmBh.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-09-07","agreeCount":11,"discussionCount":0}